The evidence with the title 'Does Obama have a 'dog-trainer on retainer for $102,000 a year at ... ' says Jun 18, 2014  ... We and others debunked the claim that Bo flew on his own airplane. In reality, the airport in Waterville, Maine, could not accommodate Obama's usual airplane, so Obama and his staff flew into a different airport on separate jets, one of which carried several members of Obama's presidential staff and Bo. 
